headline: Tuesday's big stock stories: What’s likely to move the market in the next trading session
summary: The Dow Industrials touched an all-time high and closed at a record Monday after the U.S. captured Venezuela's president over the weekend.

headline: Camden Stock Rallies 7.3% in Three Months: Will It Continue to Gain?
